ion triggers 4. Different paths for different customer behaviors 5. Integration points between ManyChat, Instagram, and the sales page Use a professional flowchart style with clear arrows, decision diamonds, process rectangles, and different colors for different stages. Include icons or symbols to represent Instagram, ManyChat, email, and purchases. Make it easy to understand and follow the logical flow. Generated Images (3) Generated 9/30/2025, 8:29:28 PM Generated 9/30/2025, 8:29:28 PM Generated 9/30/2025, 8:29:28 PM File Changes (5) 5_step_framework_workflow.png /home/user/output/5_step_framework_workflow.png Download 9/30/2025, 8:26:38 PM v1 image/png customer_journey_flowchart.png /home/user/output/customer_journey_flowchart.png Download 9/30/2025, 8:25:54 PM v1 image/png deliverables_summary.md /home/user/output/deliverables_summary.md Download 9/30/2025, 8:29:28 PM v1 text/markdown integration_diagram.png /home/user/output/integration_diagram.png Download 9/30/2025, 8:27:13 PM v1 image/png manychat_knowledge_base.html /home/user/output/manychat_knowledge_base.html Download 9/30/2025, 8:28:59 PM v1 text/html Notebook notebook_9BGcg.ipynb notebook_9BGcg.ipynb Download 4/15/2026, 12:25:34 PM v1 application/x-ipynb+json Perfect! Now let me create the ManyChat automation flow diagrams: Using Tool | Programmatic Visualization Create a detailed ManyChat automation flow diagram showing: 1. Trigger setup for \"I'm ready\" messages and comment responses 2. The complete automated sequence from initial contact to sale 3. Different conversation paths based on user responses 4. Email/SMS capture points 5. Follow-up sequences for abandoned conversations 6. Conditional logic and branching paths 7. Integration with landing page visits Use a conversational flow style with chat bubbles, decision trees, and automation icons. Show the exact messages and responses that would be sent. Include timing delays and conditions for each step. Generated Images (3) Generated 9/30/2025, 8:33