ers and get automated response</td> +    </tr> +    <tr> +      <td>Build Initial Flow</td> +      <td>Create 4-message welcome sequence</td> +      <td>Welcome messages and landing page URL</td> +      <td>Complete automated conversation flow</td> +      <td>20 minutes</td> +      <td>Flow sends all 4 messages in correct order</td> +    </tr> +    <tr> +      <td>Add Email Capture</td> +      <td>Insert email input card and connect to email service</td> +      <td>Email service API or Zapier connection</td> +      <td>Working email collection system</td> +      <td>15 minutes</td> +      <td>Test emails are captured and stored correctly</td> +    </tr> +    <tr> +      <td>Set Follow-up Timing</td> +      <td>Configure 24hr, 3-day, and 7-day delayed messages</td> +      <td>Follow-up message templates</td> +      <td>Timed sequence automation</td> +      <td>15 minutes</td> +      <td>Follow-up messages send at correct intervals</td> +    </tr> +    <tr> +      <td>Create FAQ Responses</td> +      <td>Set up auto-replies for common questions</td> +      <td>List of frequently asked questions</td> +      <td>Instant FAQ response system</td> +      <td>10 minutes</td> +      <td>FAQ keywords trigger appropriate responses</td> +    </tr> +  </tbody> +</table> + +      <div class=\"checklist\"> +        <h5>ManyChat Message Templates:</h5> +        <p><strong>Message 1 (Immediate):</strong><br> +        \"Thanks for your interest! 🙌 I'm excited to share this with you...\"</p> + +        <p><strong>Message 2 (5 seconds delay):</strong><br> +        \"Here's exactly what you'll get: [Brief 2-3 line benefit summary]\"</p> + +        <p><strong>Message 3 (10 seconds delay):</strong><br> +        \"Check it out here: [YOUR LANDING PAGE LINK]\"</p> + +        <p><strong>Message 4 (30 seconds delay):</strong><br> +        \"What's your best email so I can send you the bonus materials? 📧\"</p> + +        <h5>Follow-up Sequence Templates:</h5> +        <p><strong>24-Hour Follow